It's really incredible to me the ease I have now to be in tree pose or downward dog. I used to be so unbalanced and even lifting one knee up for tree pose was hard to me and now some time later and some yoga classes later it makes me so incredibly happy to be in tree and lift my hands up and stay in this pose. Same with down dog, it used to be really uncomfortable and I wanted to change position asap. Now, my feet touch the ground and I can stay in it with ease and smile on my face. I think hearing so many people say that and actually experiencing that for yourself is so different, I didn't think I would be one of those people who will be able to do that!
